Package com.pionix.controllers

Interface IDbController<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - data type to be controlled
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AdministratorController, BranchController, BranchEmployeeController, CustomerController, DbController, ShipmentController, TransportationPersonnelController, UserController
    public interface IDbController<T>
    Interface for DbControllers A DbController should have basic operations like get, delete, update, create, size, listing This is the interface for them
